snippet.title: Record Run Gameplay Trailer - Available Now!
snippet.description:
Play NOW for free! - https://itunes.apple.com/app/record-run/id833795526
For more info: http://www.recordrun.com


Record Run is a level-based runner from Harmonix, the makers of Rock Band, Dance Central, and VidRhythm.  Dodge obstacles to the beat in a crazy musical world set to YOUR music! Record Run creates gameplay levels from songs you load into the game.
